{"tid":866748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國男傷人後跑水族館 跳進鯊魚池裸泳","createTime":"2018-10-18T06:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T10:07:42.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b18b9efc3d80da77622361321b57bbd47a46559c","tid":866748,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181018/_2018101812213899627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181018%2F_2018101812213899627.jpg&h=fb094e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">加國男子傷人後跑進水族館，跳進鯊魚池裸泳被捕。（網圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多一名涉嫌傷人的男子，跑到瑞普利水族館（Ripley&rsquo;s Aquarium）跳進鯊魚池裸泳，影片在社交媒體上瘋傳。警方稱該名男子涉及一宗暴力傷人案，已被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據報，一名卑詩省男子於上周五（12日）參觀水族館期間，竟脫掉衣服跳入鯊魚池中游泳，警方接報到場調查，並稱該名男子與日前發生的一宗暴力傷人案有關。經過調查發現男子名叫韋弗（David Weaver），37歲，來自卑詩省，警方於周二在安省雷灣（Thunder Bay）把他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n當時水族館的一名遊客把韋弗裸泳的影片發布到Youtube上，該長達1分鐘的影片顯示，韋弗在眾目睽睽之下，越過鯊魚池的安全屏障，脫光所有衣服，一個後翻，跳入水族館內最大的鯊魚池。韋弗在池中蛙泳，而沙虎鯨就在距離他腳下僅數厘米處。魚池中還有綠色鋸鰩、海龜、海鰻等十多種海洋動物。不到1分鐘，水族館員工則要求韋弗出來，他也乖乖就範。<br />\n<br />\n多倫多警方發現，韋弗還牽涉一宗暴力傷人案，準備安排把韋弗送往多倫多。該宗暴力攻擊事件發生在當晚八點左右，位於展覽廣場的中世紀（Medieval Times）景點外。警方稱，受害者嚴重受傷，施襲者其後前往距離東部約5公里的水族館。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fWWOUkLrBjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfWWOUkLrBjw&d=1VW3aCcIKcO1RNMqTwAeg9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a0d8a6f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fWWOUkLrBjw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/843325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F843325&d=1VW3aCcIKcO1RNMqTwAeg9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=32f4d10b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F843325&h=b54f8b32\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/843325</a>"},{"pid":"b36546bce6b845a1610633b32941e30ac89bd044","tid":866748,"uid":21886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"yolo"},{"pid":"a5e9700602c7ca61f0dca5212022c7d05001c130","tid":866748,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"咁撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef98e1c122d36318553eaa84235d8dedb0c2f634","tid":866748,"uid":34466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"表演花式自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18165e3b7c01eb32f53ed7ec254cbc10822a539","tid":866748,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"乜咁好彩d鯊魚喂到飽晒"}]}